overview: This semester, Ashlynn looks to join a sorority, but before she joins the club, she gets to experience firsthand what it's like to be a pledge. Made to cross the line repeatedly, Ashlynn starts to suck and fuck her way up the ranks of the sisterhood. Can she handle it? Or will the rigors of a rock hard cock push her over the edge...
tagline: This Time Around...They Never Expected This Of Her!
title: Ashlynn Goes to College 2
